My take on NToV is this, if Aary spawns, you take him out.  For instance, if Aary isn't due to spawn until Wednesday, you can Raid whatever you want til Aary spawns, then you better be in NToV.  If you run out of spawns (Spawns are spread out), you may leave NToV, but you forfeit sole rights, and NToV Becomes FiF.   <p>Malkier Shadowhealer<br>
