<br>
However we also had it aligned with patch days as close as possible, so you usually had your turn start on a patch day.  It's when patches started getting farther between and spawns get spread out over days and days and all the nail-biters started picking apart the semantics of the rules that NToV and the rotation got to be more trouble that it was worth.<br>
<br>
